  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical performance study is being conducted to evaluate the performance of the Aptima
      Herpes Simplex Viruses 1 &amp; 2 assay for detection of herpes simplex virus (HSV) type 1 (HSV-1)
      and HSV type 2 (HSV-2) in swab samples prospectively collected from suspected HSV lesions.
      Specimens collected using swabs from viral transport medium (VTM)collection kits and Aptima
      swab collection kits will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
