  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Evaluation of sensitivity and specificity of the Aptima HSV 1 &amp; 2 Assay on Panther</measure>
    <time_frame>1 day</time_frame>
    <description>Sensitivity and specificity of the Aptima HSV 1 &amp; 2 assay will be determined by comparing assay results to results from a reference method representing the true infected status of the subjects. Sensitivity will be reported as the percentage of subjects with an HSV infection who test positive by the Aptima HSV 1 &amp; 2 assay. Specificity will be reported as the percentage of subjects without an HSV infection who test negative by the Aptima HSV 1 &amp; 2 assay.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
